These codes will give the band gap 

File:  gap_ispin_1.sh is for non-spin-polarized calculations 
File:  gap_ispin_2.sh is for spin-polarized calculations (collinear)

### USE as
$  bash gap_ispin_1.sh OUTCAR

$  bash gap_ispin_2.sh       ## in the folder where OSZICAR and OUTCAR files are available
